Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:05.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,what did you say？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:07.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:12.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,why do you say？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:17.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,刃を砥ぐ、微睡む
