Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:35.69,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,final white heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:39.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,さあ奪い合うよ傷を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:41.24,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I don’t know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:43.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I don’t know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:47.87,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,survive of vision
